Project Requirements
Using the Java programming language, an gift editor must be designed, and built, that allows a user to carry out certain tasks. The tasks are outlined here:
Tasks
Create individual questions (true/false, multiple choice etc)
Build a series of questions of a particular type. (e.g. 10 multiple-choice questions)
Save (or append) the questions to a new (existing) text file.
Some time must be spent of the design of the GUI. Included in the project folder are some screenshots of a prototype GUI for the assignment (with screen shots for True/False,Multiple Choice and Matching questions ).